12. UK Regulatory Framework and HSE Alignment 
Health and Safety at Work etc. Act 1974 (HSWA) 
• Duty to provide safe systems of work 
Management of Health and Safety at Work Regulations 1999 (MHSWR) 
• Requires risk assessment and control measures 
Construction (Design and Management) Regulations 2015 (CDM) 
• Requires planning and safe execution of construction work 
 
HSE Guidance 
• HSG65: Managing for Health and Safety 
• INDG163: Risk Assessment Guidance 
 
 

